            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "思格新能IPO在港售股超購1101倍 1手中籤率2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">股份將於今日掛牌的思格新能(06656)公布招股結果，在港公開發售部份獲1102.05倍認購，1手中籤率2%；國際配售也獲31.2倍認購。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：思格新能官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI_source-web_Sigenergy-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：思格新能官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI_source-web_Sigenergy-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：思格新能官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股昨天暗盤已顯著造好，輝立交易平台顯示，思格新能昨天暗盤收報578元，較招股價324.2元高78.3%；富途交易平台顯示的暗盤收報598元，較招股價更高84.5%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15878984-%e6%80%9d%e6%a0%bc%e6%96%b0%e8%83%bdipo%e5%9c%a8%e6%b8%af%e5%94%ae%e8%82%a1%e8%b6%85%e8%b3%bc1101%e5%80%8d-1%e6%89%8b%e4%b8%ad%e7%b1%a4%e7%8e%872",
